   5:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   * @brief   TIM HAL module driver.
   6:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *          This file provides firmware functions to manage the following
   7:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *          functionalities of the Timer Extended peripheral:
   8:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *           + Time Hall Sensor Interface Initialization
   9:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *           + Time Hall Sensor Interface Start
  10:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *           + Time Complementary signal break and dead time configuration
  11:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *           + Time Master and Slave synchronization configuration
  12:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *           + Time Output Compare/PWM Channel Configuration (for channels 5 and 6)
  13:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *           + Time OCRef clear configuration
  14:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *           + Timer remapping capabilities configuration
  15:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *           + Timer encoder index configuration
